&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; data-src=&#34;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/k1t0111/blog/main/image/20240628165637.png&#34; alt=&#34;image.png&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
